---
// Hero Section
---

<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="hero-layout">
    <div class="hero-sidebar" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="hero-main">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-kicker label fade-in-up">
          Research × Product × Taste
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="hero-title fade-in-up">
          我想把前沿 AI 的能力，<br/>做成真正有感觉、有价值的产品。
        </h1>
        
        <p class="subtitle fade-in-up hero-subtitle">
          浙江大学计算机在读，辅修金融。正在生成式模型、扩散语言模型与智能体持续学习的交叉地带工作，也持续通过项目、写作与设计练习产品判断和体验表达。
        </p>

        <div class="tags flex gap-md fade-in-up hero-tags">
          <span class="tag">理解模型</span>
          <span class="tag">产品判断</span>
          <span class="tag">审美表达</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-facts flex justify-between fade-in-up hero-facts">
        <span>Zhejiang University, CS & Finance</span>
        <span>Class of 2027</span>
        <span>UCLA / NUS Collaboration</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100dvh;
    padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-sm));
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  @supports not (height: 100dvh) {
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
  }

  .hero-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-main {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-content {
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    padding-block: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .hero-title {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  .subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    max-width: 100%;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    transition-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  .tags {
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-body);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .hero-tags {
    transition-delay: 0.3s;
  }

  .tag {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .tag:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: "—";
    position: absolute;
    right: calc(var(--space-md) * -0.5 - 0.5em);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .quick-facts {
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-ui);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .hero-facts {
    transition-delay: 0.4s;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .hero-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .quick-facts {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .tag:not(:last-child)::after {
      display: none;
    }
    .tags {
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }
</style>
